                            <comment id="98115" author="adilger" created="Fri, 31 Oct 2014 23:11:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Roland, apologies that we didn&apos;t see the patch here.  I agree it would have been better to see and land it before more people hit the bug, but at least it was fixed in 2.6, and is scheduled to land for 2.5.4 also.&lt;/p&gt;

